      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:6:1",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/13/14",
      "text": [
        "١٣. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): إِذَا وَصَلَتْ إِلَيْكُمْ أَطْرَافُ النِّعَمِ فَلَا تُنَفِّرُوا أَقْصَاهَا بِقِلَّةِ الشُّكْرِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "13. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: When you get (only) small favours do not push them away through lack of gratefulness."
        ]
      }
    },
